OL,12,FTinder, was jailed after defrauding    
OL,13,Ffour women out of about #80,000.       
OL,15,FOne victim said Gray, from West        
OL,16,FYorkshire, "totally ruined my life" and
OL,17,Fleft her with significant trust issues.
